{"tid":1574860,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［預左比人屌］請大家唔好忘記初心","createTime":"2019-09-16T15:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T18:03:17.000Z","uid":199669,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"76e7220d7abad71ef26be606d7a71bd589abd8ff","tid":1574860,"uid":199669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:12:17.000Z","msg":"無錯反擊對我地而言真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都射左幾次<br />\n但遁例都要提醒翻巴打們唔好衝動 唔好亂用自己既拳頭<br />\n一開始上街既目的係為左守護香港<br />\n一開始反擊既目的係為左保護手足<br />\n香港人係overwatch守望者<br />\n<br />\n攻擊既時候唔好打頭，黑社會死不足昔但係我怕巴打會留低心理陰影<br />\n為左垃圾福建幫，真係唔值<br />\n<br />\n可以放過，但千奇唔好殺錯。我地唔係政府，更加唔係黑警。<br />\n<br />\n武力應該以擊倒為主，可以4,5個人上，人多係因為我地團結，但20個圍一個睇落真係好難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c852ae1c008a117eedfecdff06b46c8e5474807","tid":1574860,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3d6990649f8943ddbcda1de815cd158bb1071cf","tid":1574860,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"915國旗行動好成功!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573307</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jR5wr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jR5wr1.jpg&h=d9b2c693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46158fe479e00fc0611aad8ed98c33197d987792","tid":1574860,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ee5617ac3d07645b0e81560b95c595e7c54d35","tid":1574860,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0763d6bad1322f9596fc58ea9e6977e02f513050","tid":1574860,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:1